item.title: Injured Livingstone ruled out of remainder of Pakistan Test series
item.description: Injured Livingstone ruled out of remainder of Pakistan Test series Rawalpindi: England all-rounder Liam Livingstone was Monday ruled out of the remainder of the Test series against Pakistan after sustaining a right knee injury during the first match here.
